<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fragile-adj">fragile <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'frædʒaɪl/    美 /'frædʒl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-delicate">1.★ <strong>易碎的；易损坏的 (delicate)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the fragile china / glass 
易碎的瓷器/玻璃</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>脆弱的；虚弱的；体质弱的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>fragile relationship / economy</strong>
脆弱的关系/经济</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The old lady looks very fragile.
这位老太太看起来很虚弱。</p></div></div>